## How to Run
1. Install dependencies: pip install pandas sqlalchemy pymysql openpyxl
2. Set up MySQL locally, create database: CREATE DATABASE salesdb;
3. Update the connection string in the notebook with your password
4. Run all cells in the notebook
5. Open Power BI and connect to MySQL localhost → salesdb → sales_data
